        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="字符串常用函数"><a href="#字符串常用函数" class="headerlink" title="字符串常用函数"></a>字符串常用函数</h3><pre><code>其中str为目标字符串str.lower()：将字符全改为小写str.upper()：将字符全改为大写str.split( sep = none )：返回一个列表，由str根据sep分割的部分组成str.count(sub)：返回子串在str中出现的次数str.replace(old,new)：返回字符串副本，所有old子串被替换成newstr.center(width[,fillchar])：字符串str根据width宽度居中str.strip(chars)：从str中去除chars中列出的字符str.join(iter)：在iter变量除最后元素之外每个元素后面增加一个iter例：&quot;,&quot;join(&quot;12345&quot;)结果：&quot;1,2,3,4,5&quot;</code></pre><h3 id="字符串类型的格式化"><a href="#字符串类型的格式化" class="headerlink" title="字符串类型的格式化"></a>字符串类型的格式化</h3><p>使用：&lt;字符串&gt;.format</p><p><img src="C:\Users\86188\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220425204954612.png" alt="image-20220425204954612"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\86188\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220425205210715.png" alt="image-20220425205210715"></p><h3 id="time库的使用"><a href="#time库的使用" class="headerlink" title="time库的使用"></a>time库的使用</h3><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python">时间获取：time<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>ctime<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>gmtime<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>时间格式化：strftime<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>strptiem<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>程序计时：sleep<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>perf_counter<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><h4 id="基本时间函数"><a href="#基本时间函数" class="headerlink" title="基本时间函数"></a>基本时间函数</h4><p>time()：获取当前时间戳，即计算机内部时间值，浮点数</p><p>ctime()：获取当前时间并以易读方式表示，返回字符串</p><p>gmtime()：获取当前时间，表示为计算机可处理的时间格式</p><h4 id="时间格式化"><a href="#时间格式化" class="headerlink" title="时间格式化"></a>时间格式化</h4><p>strftime()：tpl是格式化模板字符串，用来定义输出效果，ts是计算机内部时间类型变量</p><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python">t <span class="token operator">=</span> time<span class="token punctuation">.</span>gmtime<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>time<span class="token punctuation">.</span>strftime<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>t<span class="token punctuation">)</span>输出：<span class="token string">'2022-01-26 12:55:20'</span></code></pre><p>strptime()：</p><pre><code>timestr = &#39;2018-01-26 12:55:20&#39;time.strptime(timestr,&quot;%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S&quot;)</code></pre><p><img src="C:\Users\86188\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220425212806125.png" alt="image-20220425212806125"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\86188\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220425212658117.png" alt="image-20220425212658117"></p><h4 id="程序计时"><a href="#程序计时" class="headerlink" title="程序计时"></a>程序计时</h4><p>sleep(s)：s为休眠时间，单位是秒，可以是浮点数</p><p>perf_counter()：返回一个CPU级别的精确时间计数值，单位为秒，由于这个计数起点不确定，连续调用差值才有意义</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
